{"tid":1418784,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非人士，你地要誠實面對一件事，就係你地係咪開始因為武力升級而令香港陷入準戰爭狀態，而令你既利益受損？","createTime":"2019-08-05T20:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T11:45:37.000Z","uid":167938,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"12fde56301a51bc3bd3fb1a43cd6df8488505368","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:25:51.000Z","msg":"1) 勇武人士武力升級，令警方有使用更高武力的藉口，最後會令解放軍南下，令「一國兩制」變成真正的「謊言」會令經濟插水式下降。大部分和理非的人都不是為理想放棄吃飯的人，點到即止重新令香港政權經濟穩定是最重要。<br />\n<br />\n2) 非暴力只是犬儒文化<br />\n一滴血都不用流的革命在世界上不存在<br />\n咁就證明左 和理非係 為左逃避痛苦而做 和理非<br />\n<br />\n3）理想是五大訴求一一實現，現實係無一兌現。<br />\n係咁既情況下要犧牲我的時間金錢去為呢五個無法兌現既訴求 實為不智！ 香港人最好是以不破壞經濟基礎而向政權「要求」<br />\n<br />\n我呢個post絕對唔係要搞分化<br />\n而係想和理非既人諗下 今時今日既和理非係唔係要繼續做和理非？咁樣對場運動仲有無幫助？<br />\n希望後排既人諗清楚！係咪要繼續做和理非<br />\n可唔可以為場運動付出多啲？香港你同我都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鳩打但只想表達一件事<br />\n就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢一種絕對係分化Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n唔知同上萬個正皮個個post有無得比<br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武派 唔需要將你地自己既價值 <br />\n建基於一個分化post之上<br />\n如果你認為勇武係正確的事 請繼續努力<br />\n我係前線中游 絕對明白勇武既痛苦同恐懼<br />\n跟本只有太愛香港既人至會願意為香港流血<br />\n<br />\n和理非 你亦都唔需要因為勇武升級而指責割席<br />\n香港人行到呢步 得來不易 <br />\n如果你覺得勇武既人阻到你為香港爭取五大訴求<br />\n請記得話我知 我逐條前線幫你同佢地講<br />\n我咁講並無唔認同和理非<br />\n因為大家都知和理非係勇武派最強後盾<br />\n<br />\n香港人 好老土講我地只係輸剩<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">團結</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行到今日先黎真正分化 咁樣點對得住比人拉告暴動既兄弟姊妹？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我想問下 <br />\n比人拉左既人同以死控告個七位義士<br />\n佢地有無分和理非定勇武？<br />\n<br />\n不指責 不割席 不督灰 不受傷 不被捕 不流血<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請記住呢六不</span><br />\n<br />\n係香港人贏既惟一希望！"},{"pid":"6ed6411a8a22ae448f4a888a25feb11db840e52d","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:28:58.000Z","msg":"前線勇武義士, 我覺得你地要誠實面對一樣野, 你地係咪開始迷失同享受權力?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417502</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dfd5e3e4c2fbef6f7bf3f9d18558ae7aba351f09","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:29:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ea59876c53d66985b5ada731c6a8d366ad7afcb","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:30:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4947cb78bddfe5058f36fdbc2252446f2072195","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:30:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32a31215c42f8860b72d71aeaf76238af87621ef","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:31:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49f4662e18e194f533f98e1024c36d8d92daf68f","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:32:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1f5562534d85f426ccc9264ae584d93774cb482","tid":1418784,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:34:28.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"40176349e6230b47c6d9427a018ee4fc16f2064f","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:34:33.000Z","msg":"請幫忙推"},{"pid":"3ac85691f8b0c6c5fdbac1d9fdeaff10a2bf11ba","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:34:53.000Z","msg":"呢個post我諗左8個鐘"},{"pid":"6118b14f74d496e56cb4960e4d4afda17d3e49cd","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:35:12.000Z","msg":"係咪好戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住"},{"pid":"8be6c5da3b4fd7207a2a7fdfb0279e42e40d4b22","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:35:37.000Z","msg":"我唔想輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以先搞咁多野 唔訓教"},{"pid":"6d4ca33dc6f8748dcbb0fcc5032cf3d2b5321df2","tid":1418784,"uid":272243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:35:44.000Z","msg":"講唔分化既分化post係做咩事"},{"pid":"a11bd26d6ce7623977c7d847d284ba826e2d383d","tid":1418784,"uid":217103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:35:44.000Z","msg":"辛苦大家喇！但我想提返你哋一樣嘢！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418774</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家記得返 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時代革命</span>意思<br />\n點解用時代而唔係世代<br />\n係因為呢個係一整個時代嘅抗爭 <br />\n包咗唔同generation 唔同嘅階層<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港時代革命！</span>"},{"pid":"e1fe00714e71c1aa58c6d5e568f1db6a5852fb54","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d4ca33dc6f8748dcbb0fcc5032cf3d2b5321df2","tid":1418784,"uid":272243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:35:44.000Z","msg":"講唔分化既分化post係做咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:36:53.000Z","msg":"我係想話比大家知 要打個分化post出黎唔難<br />\n尤其係亂局時 大家頭腦都被沖昏"},{"pid":"c2530b9fb28e01b11d2849d12ed28aa78a598c3e","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:37:29.000Z","msg":"上半段係鳩作<br />\n為左扮個分化post<br />\n就好似話勇武「戀權」個個post咁"},{"pid":"1a9db047558d4ad4059cdcac91d424b18fcc2848","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:38:34.000Z","msg":"想大家分到咩係為分化而分化<br />\n<br />\n我地團結返好唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df00f0002f0e0713a249cc0216a56b9a536dbb5","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:39:52.000Z","msg":"如果呢個post無用 咁由佢啦<br />\n我都係想盡一分綿力 團結咁多巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住 我可能太攰<br />\n唔知點先可以化解到大家既矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6201ac81737d5b07d483f7b2eec53d68feddd1","tid":1418784,"uid":2908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:40:09.000Z","msg":"最重要係團結<br />\n呢個先係重點"},{"pid":"74200ffd5348077036272b6ce1f5fab5b431c303","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:42:03.000Z","msg":"多謝10位巴絲比正皮<br />\n我捱唔住要訓了....明天見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19557cc19a251ee321889d62dd89f206d5e3ed6","tid":1418784,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:44:54.000Z","msg":"都係既 每個人有唔同諗法<br />\n大家明明目標一致 點解要指責"},{"pid":"b0833f1df2f22b14026a57f228fd103453d0c479","tid":1418784,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:45:22.000Z","msg":"就係要依d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心覺得係差在唔夠團結，只要大家齊心，用咩方法都好，和理或勇武都必贏。"},{"pid":"f56e76154fb28a3decc104275e79bd3ea5735ea6","tid":1418784,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:50:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21db08ddeb5ac5fb8ba35cb3e554a9a9799ce8da","tid":1418784,"uid":85439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:12:50.000Z","msg":"太標題太曲 玩死自己友。。。唔好推由佢沉啦"},{"pid":"e1c09ecc8601874b8d5fb19dc5ab7e670ba0bed6","tid":1418784,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21db08ddeb5ac5fb8ba35cb3e554a9a9799ce8da","tid":1418784,"uid":85439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:12:50.000Z","msg":"太標題太曲 玩死自己友。。。唔好推由佢沉啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:31:57.000Z","msg":"唔係掛<br />\n<br />\n大大隻紅字已經"}]}